# Cute Mini Tomato Pomodoro Timer

Creation of a cute, desktop-widget-style Pomodoro timer using Electron. The app will feature a frameless, transparent window that sits on the desktop, with a premium glassmorphic aesthetic and a "cute tomato" mascot.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> - **Figma MCP**: I don't have direct access to a "Figma MCP" in my current environment. If you have a Figma design link, please share it and I can try to read the design using browser tools. Otherwise, I will proceed with the design inspired by the generated image.
> - **Always on Top**: The widget will be configured to stay on top of other windows by default.
> - **Draggable**: The entire widget will be draggable from anywhere on the tomato or the transparent glass.

## Proposed Changes

