### Frontend (Renderer)
- [NEW] `index.html`: Structure for the tomato mascot, timer display, and controls.
- [NEW] `style.css`: Premium CSS with glassmorphism, animations, and the tomato character styling.
- [NEW] `renderer.js`: Timer logic, state management (Work/Break), and interaction handling.

### Assets
- [NEW] `assets/tomato.svg` (or CSS implementation): A high-quality SVG/CSS representation of the cute tomato.

